1
00:00:03,536 --> 00:00:04,838
Is this really enough for you?

2
00:00:09,209 --> 00:00:10,209
Why are you acting

3
00:00:10,210 --> 00:00:11,745
like some tragic hero?

4
00:00:14,214 --> 00:00:16,116
No wonder your A-You left you.

5
00:00:20,019 --> 00:00:21,019
So, are you really

6
00:00:21,454 --> 00:00:23,423
satisfied with being strangers?

7
00:00:30,597 --> 00:00:31,597
If you like him,

8
00:00:32,532 --> 00:00:33,532
why not just say it?

9
00:00:37,003 --> 00:00:38,003
If I don't say anything,

10
00:00:38,505 --> 00:00:39,706
there's no hope to be had,

11
00:00:40,907 --> 00:00:42,387
but there's no disappointment either.

12
00:00:46,980 --> 00:00:48,281
I'm asking you one last time.

13
00:00:50,116 --> 00:00:51,917
Say it or don't.

14
00:00:57,257 --> 00:00:58,257
Fine.

15
00:00:59,092 --> 00:01:00,092
I'll say it.

16
00:01:01,261 --> 00:01:02,661
I like you. I really like you.

17
00:01:02,662 --> 00:01:03,695
I'm crazy about you.

18
00:01:03,696 --> 00:01:04,963
I can't stop checking up on you.

19
00:01:04,964 --> 00:01:06,231
I remember every single thing

20
00:01:06,232 --> 00:01:07,332
you've ever said to me.

21
00:01:07,333 --> 00:01:08,734
I didn't know the first thing about it,

22
00:01:08,735 --> 00:01:09,935
but I joined this industry just for you.

23
00:01:09,936 --> 00:01:10,537
But...

24
00:01:10,538 --> 00:01:11,704
I just didn't want...

25
00:01:22,449 --> 00:01:23,483
They say we hug

26
00:01:23,783 --> 00:01:25,584
to make up for the fact

27
00:01:25,585 --> 00:01:27,620
that the right side of
the heart doesn't beat.

28
00:01:36,996 --> 00:01:38,531
Are you even a man?

29
00:01:39,365 --> 00:01:40,432
I thought

30
00:01:40,433 --> 00:01:41,567
you were just using me.

31
00:01:41,568 --> 00:01:42,836
I was miserable for days.

32
00:01:43,236 --> 00:01:44,756
How are you going to make it up to me?

33
00:01:51,945 --> 00:01:52,946
Well,

34
00:01:54,614 --> 00:01:56,482
how about I give myself to you?

35
00:01:56,483 --> 00:01:57,717
Will you take me?

36
00:01:59,419 --> 00:02:00,720
Who'd want you?

37
00:02:01,087 --> 00:02:02,322
You're so big.

38
00:02:03,223 --> 00:02:04,556
It would cost a fortune

39
00:02:04,557 --> 00:02:05,992
just to keep you fed.

40
00:02:23,009 --> 00:02:24,042
So...

41
00:02:24,043 --> 00:02:26,379
my number one fan since my debut...

42
00:02:27,413 --> 00:02:28,413
was you all along?

43
00:02:30,583 --> 00:02:32,718
I was also that "Black &amp; White" superfan

44
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:33,999
who used to butt heads with you.

45
00:02:35,989 --> 00:02:37,557
You ignored the real guy

46
00:02:38,091 --> 00:02:39,659
just to ship the CP?

47
00:02:41,127 --> 00:02:43,062
I was just afraid of holding you back.

48
00:02:47,300 --> 00:02:48,701
I used to care about that,

49
00:02:49,369 --> 00:02:50,203
but now,

50
00:02:50,204 --> 00:02:51,437
I just want to be happy.

51
00:02:52,772 --> 00:02:54,641
I don't want to live a lie.

52
00:02:55,275 --> 00:02:57,076
I want us to be out in the open.

53
00:03:18,631 --> 00:03:19,766
Whoa, isn't this a bit fast?

54
00:03:20,266 --> 00:03:21,568
You haven't even confessed yet,

55
00:03:22,735 --> 00:03:24,455
and you're already taking your clothes off?

56
00:03:26,072 --> 00:03:27,907
I thought you could feel it.

57
00:03:28,708 --> 00:03:29,708
I love you.

58
00:03:30,877 --> 00:03:31,877
Are you willing?
